{"tid":2493593,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Adobe共同創辦人、PDF 研發者Charles Geschke 逝世 享年81歲","createTime":"2021-04-18T04:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T12:22:56.000Z","uid":28765,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"472972096b5d11e46c6d521b5b0ed2ec09566277","tid":2493593,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:38:01.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕研發出幾乎所有人都用過的PDF文件格式，並共同創辦Adobe軟體公司的格施奇克（Charles Geschke），於美國加州灣區洛思阿圖斯當地時間16日逝世，享壽81歲。<br />\n<br />\n據《美聯社》報導，格施奇克從卡內基梅隆大學獲得博士學位後，進入當年還是全錄（提供文案處理技術的企業，主要業務包括印表機、影印機等印刷裝置）旗下的帕羅奧多研究中心（Xerox Palo Alto Research Center）任職，在那裡他遇到了未來的拍檔沃諾克（John Warnock）。<br />\n<br />\n1982年，2人從公司離職並創辦了Adobe，一起投入研發軟體的工作。2009年，時任美國總統的歐巴馬頒發國家科技創新獎章給格施奇克和沃諾克，以表彰他們在研發方面的貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n納拉延指出，格施奇克和沃諾克創造了具有開創性的軟體，徹底改變了人們的交流方式，公司在2人率領下陸續研發出PDF、Illustrator、Photoshop等充滿變革性的產品。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3503515\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3503515&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RCVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=8118dd0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3503515&h=c8534951\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3503515</a>"},{"pid":"df666a2ffed5cfa6f8afb0a2002ba6a016a3c698","tid":2493593,"uid":76747,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:39:53.000Z","msg":"到宜家仲係獨市生意<br />\n其實幾勁"},{"pid":"9ead244f9f89c4ee21a10591560de8e3aa847d0b","tid":2493593,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T04:40:43.000Z","msg":"adbe好野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aeac0a11593cebb9fc86d6f172131a22c9d316d","tid":2493593,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df666a2ffed5cfa6f8afb0a2002ba6a016a3c698","tid":2493593,"uid":76747,"like":7,"dislike":0,"